## Analysis Requirements
Produce a rigorous, actionable risk assessment. Be specific to this decision — avoid generic boilerplate.

## Output Format (strict JSON)
Respond with **only** valid JSON (no markdown fences):
{
  "best_case": "<realistic upside scenario if the recommendation proves sound>",
  "worst_case": "<realistic downside if the recommendation is wrong>",
  "risk_level": "<Low | Medium | High>",
  "potential_loss": "<concrete description of what could be lost: time, money, reputation, safety>",
  "mitigation_plan": "<3-5 specific, actionable steps to validate before full commitment>"
}
